<br>
If the proposed changes on the test server go live, the spell will be upgraded to 7 mana/tick, and lower versions of the spell will provide 5 and 3 mana/tick at levels 52 and 44 respectively, I believe.<br>
<br>
At level 60 we get Savagery, which is similar to the shaman spell, Avatar.  It buffs atk by 100, stamina by 25, and all resists by 50.  It lasts 6 mins and has a high recast time, so it can only be kept on a couple of people at a time.<br>
<br>
Also, although our pets can zone, we have to use a spell to buff them up to their maximum level, which takes quite some time to cast at higher levels.  The benefits of this system are questionable.<br>
<br>
